EN: I found a big shell on the beach.

ZH: 这个贝壳有漂亮的花纹。
EN: This shell has a pretty pattern.

ZH: 孩子们在沙滩上找到了许多贝壳。
EN: The kids found many shells on the beach.

ZH: 珍惜每一个美丽的贝壳吧。
EN: Treasure every beautiful shell.

ZH: 那片海滩上遍布着各种各样的贝壳。
EN: Various kinds of shells cover that beach.

ZH: 每一个贝壳都有它独特的形状。
EN: Every shell has its unique shape.

